      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    HMCTS heads online for 2020 Public User Event
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Summary of content and information from the fourth annual event that was held remotely over three days.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
